text: Singham ( or Wells, J. C. (2008). Longman Pronunciation Dictionary, 3rd edn, Harlow, UK: LongmanDaniel Jones, Peter Roach, et al. (2011). Cambridge Pronouncing Dictionary, 18th edn, Cambridge, UK: Cambridge University Press) is a suburban town in East London, England. Plaistow North and Plaistow South are two of the ten electoral wards making up the UK parliamentary constituency of West Ham. ==References== Category:Towns in London
title: Plaistow, Newham
